Description:
Idyllic Opportunity
The astute buyer seeking a boutique lifestyle wont be disappointed with this chic 3-Bed, 2-Storey townhouse just minutes to parks, shopping centre, medical centre and quality schools.
Near new and located in highly sought after Selandra Rise, this cleverly designed property is perfect for family living.
The open plan kitchen has been designed to bring depth and accessibility to the home connecting the meals area and lounge room. Prepare meals, chat at the kitchen bench or entertain in the meals area, all while watching the kids in the lounge room or playing outside in the secure yard.
Further features include-
No Body Corporate Fees;
Large master bedroom with ensuite and walk in robe;
Great size 2nd& 3rd bedrooms with double mirrored built in robes;
Quality build;
Internal access from garage;
Block out blinds throughout;
Ducted heating, split system cooling + ceiling fans;
Low maintenance yard; and
Turnkey home, nothing to but move in and enjoy.
On a low-maintenance, fully fenced block close to all the lifestyle amenities of highly desirable Clyde North, this stylish residence is sure to appeal to a wide range of buyers. Don't delay, call Candice Blanch today to arrange your inspection.
